<arggraph id="micro_c177" topic_id="only_child" stance="pro">
  <edu id="e1"><![CDATA[If you do not have any siblings, you have all the attention of your parents and do not have to share.]]></edu>
  <edu id="e2"><![CDATA[Furthermore, you don't have any sibling rivalry.]]></edu>
  <edu id="e3"><![CDATA[You don't have to argue about which TV show to watch.]]></edu>
  <edu id="e4"><![CDATA[There is no pressure to do better than some one else.]]></edu>
  <edu id="e5"><![CDATA[Furthermore you do not have to be a role model for them.]]></edu>
  <edu id="e6" implicit="true"><![CDATA[It is good to be the only child.]]></edu>
